      "title": "Yet another all-time record price for Delta Estate",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Delta Estate surpassed its previous record price of Rs. 1,000 per kg for a BP1 obtained last week and established a new all-time record price of Rs. 1,040 per kg for the same grade in the CTC Medium Grown category at this week\u2019s auction held on 20 July. This line of tea was purchased by Heritage Teas Ltd.",
        "Delta Estate located in Pupuressa comes under the purview of Pussellawa Plantations Ltd., and this line of tea was sold by broker John Keells PLC."
